# ObsidianAI — Cursor Project Rules

## Repo structure (current state)
- /legacy-static/index.html  — OLD site, do not touch
- style.css                  — COMPLETE, has all styles including #audit, .audit-layout, Stripe step styles
- script.js                  — COMPLETE, has Instant Audit Stripe flow already coded
- app.py                     — FastAPI backend on Render at https://obsidianai-evtu.onrender.com
- agent.py                   — ObsidianAgent class wrapping xAI Grok
- hospitality_agent.py       — Hotel inventory agent
- init.sql                   — PostgreSQL schema
- seed_db.py                 — local SQLite seed
- CNAME                      — obsidianai.org

## What needs to be created
- index.html at repo ROOT    — this is the ONLY missing piece for the site to go live
  - Must use all section IDs and classes that style.css and script.js already target
  - GitHub Pages serves from repo root, so root index.html = obsidianai.org

## Design system (already in style.css — match it exactly)
- Background: #000000, Text: #ffffff
- Borders: #181818 (--border), #222222 (--border-mid), #2c2c2c (--border-light)
- Green: #4ade80 (--green) — success/live states only
- Amber: #fbbf24 (--amber) — warning/stakes only
- Fonts: Syne (display), DM Mono (monospace labels) — loaded via Google Fonts
- 1px border grid layout, no rounded corners > 3px, no gradients
- --nav-h: 64px, --max-w: 1440px, --pad-x: 48px

## Sections in order (script.js and style.css target these exact IDs)
1. header — fixed nav with .logo, .nav-links, .nav-cta
2. .hero — hero with h1 and CTA buttons
3. .proof-bar — 4 stat items with .proof-item and .proof-num
4. #platform — 3 pillars + 4 .cap-card grid
5. #impact — 4 .impact-card + .impact-cta block
6. #audit — $97 Instant Audit paid product (auditStep1/2/3 must exist here)
7. #industries — 4 .industry-card grid
8. #pricing — 3 .price-card grid
9. #roadmap — 4 .roadmap-item timeline
10. #contact-form — 2-col contact + form with id="contactForm"
11. footer
12. .chat-fab + .chat-panel (Grok chat widget)

## Script.js element IDs it depends on (must exist in index.html)
Chat: chatFab, chatPanel, chatClose, chatMessages, chatIn, chatSend
Contact form: contactForm, formToast
Audit: auditStep1, auditStep2, auditStep3, auditInputForm, auditPayBtn, 
       auditBack, auditSummary, stripeCardElement, auditPayError, a-email,
       a-company, a-industry, a-size, a-stack, a-concerns
Email obfuscation: emailLink (data-u="team" data-d="obsidianai.org")
Mobile nav: navHamburger, navMobile

## Revenue priority
1. index.html creation → git push → site live → $97 audits can sell
